{"word":"G3129 - μανθάνω - manthánō - man-than'-o - Learn","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μανθάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">manthánō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">man-than'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Learn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கற்றுக்கொள், அறிந்துக்கொள், பழகு"},{"paragraph":"to learn, be apprised"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Prolonged from a primary verb, another form of which, <b>&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B8;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>matheo&#x0304;</b>, is used as an alternate in certain tenses; to <i>learn</i> (in any way): - learn, understand.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2648/2648\">G2648</a>, <a href=\"#/G3100/3100\">G3100</a>, <a href=\"#/G3101/3101\">G3101</a>, <a href=\"#/G3102/3102\">G3102</a>, <a href=\"#/G3129/3129\">G3129</a>, <a href=\"#/G4827/4827\">G4827</a>"}]}